        "dialogue": {
            "defaultDialogue": “Thank the stars, you’ve come to my rescue! I’ve been locked up in this holding cell ever since the wretched station leader intercepted my ship and confiscated the top-secret data I was transporting. The information is stored on a data drive, and I have a hunch that its being kept somewhere in the Security Room. You must get that information back to me for safe keeping, you’re my only hope! I will stay close and assist you in your mission.”,
