    "npc_jaydai" : {
        "name": "Jaydai",
        "stateDescriptions": {
            "alive": "Fear is the path to the dark side. Fear leads to anger.",
            "dead": "I lost the high ground...",
            "imprisoned": "Save me you must, my young Padawan."
        },
        "dialogue": {
            "meetDialogue": “Greetings young adventurer, I sense that the cosmic powers at play have intertwined our fates and brought us here together with a like purpose. To rid the galaxy of the seat of evil that is this wretched space station. In the interest of time, I will be forthright. The machine in the center of this room is the reactor core for the station. Any significant damage to it will undoubtedly set off a chain reaction of explosions throughout the structure, powerful enough to tear it apart for good. I will stay close and assist you in your mission.”,
            "defaultDialogue": “We should seek out some explosives. I sensed their presence in the armory earlier. Once they are in our possession, interact with the reactor to initiate the detonation sequence. You must do this only when you believe your mission here is complete and you are ready to escape. We won’t have much time to make it back to the main hangar once the countdown begins.”,
            "questStart": “Ah yes, I see you’ve retrieved an old Beam Saber from the Dark Father’s possessions. An elegant weapon from a more civilized age. You were drawn to it, yes? It must have been calling to you… interesting. I will quickly teach you the basics of Beam Saber combat. *A few moments later* That should do it, with some luck, you’ll now be able to deflect oncoming blaster fire. Shall you meet the Dark Father and engage him in combat, you may have a chance at defeating him.”,
            "questComplete": “The countdown on the explosives has begun! We must make haste to get to the main hangar and escape before this space station is destroyed!”
        },
